g.title: j3820508478
g.text: Hey Arthur, what do you think about "Fables & Frontiers?"

g.title: j692531400
g.text: Arthur, I have a favor to ask for Amir.

g.title: j1992864122
g.text: Oh, no... he got you, too?

g.title: j3784287452
g.text: He's already asked, I take it?

g.title: j689886056
g.text: He was just telling me about the game, and I said I'd ask people if they wanted to play.

g.title: j3677100601
g.text: He was telling me about this game he wants to play with everybody. Fables & Frontiers?

g.title: j2469422707
g.text: There's this dorky game he wants to play, I said I'd ask everybody to join.

g.title: j500084861
g.text: Yes, and before you ask me, I've already said no.

g.title: j1877075761
g.text: Pass, sorry. Better things to do in a warzone.

g.title: j274378139
g.text: He's on that again? I thought he gave up after Quincy started using the figurines for target practice.

g.title: j1733003747
g.text: Don't tell me. It's that Frogs & Follies thing again?

g.title: j2049543291
g.text: I think we could all use a break, don't you?

g.title: j2389321112
g.text: I think it'd mean a lot to him if we played.

g.title: j2297992580
g.text: Yeah, I'm just asking to make him happy.

g.title: j197427494
g.text: We all have our own ways to unwind. Sorry. Pass.

g.title: j3359035846
g.text: I have better things to do in a warzone. Sorry.

g.title: j255011783
g.text: He feels like the odd man out, sometimes. I think a "group game" would help him feel more like part of the pack.

g.title: j1555852594
g.text: I think showing interest in his interests would make him feel less like an outsider. Like people cared.

g.title: j2886565655
g.text: We all have our own hobbies. Pass, sorry.

g.title: j1804008302
g.text: All right... fine. I'm in. Just to try it - no long commitments.
